# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# .dockerignore — shared exclusions for all Docker builds in this monorepo.
#
# Applies to every `docker build` that uses the repo root as the build context
# (i.e. both apps/api/Dockerfile and apps/web/Dockerfile built via
# `docker build -f apps/*/Dockerfile .`).
#
# Rule: exclude anything that is either rebuilt inside the image or must never
# reach the image layer cache (secrets, local tooling state, CI artefacts).
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── VCS / CI metadata ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.git
.github
.husky

# ── Dependencies (rebuilt inside each stage) ───────────────────────────────
**/node_modules
node_modules
**/.pnpm-store
.pnpm-store

# ── Compiled artefacts (rebuilt inside each stage) ─────────────────────────
**/dist
**/.next
**/*.tsbuildinfo
**/stryker-incremental.json

# ── Environment / secrets — NEVER bake into images ─────────────────────────
.env
.env.*
**/.env
**/.env.*

# ── Test and coverage output ────────────────────────────────────────────────
**/coverage
**/reports
**/playwright-report
**/test-results
**/e2e

# ── Local dev infrastructure config (not needed at runtime) ────────────────
docker
docker-compose*.yml

# ── Documentation ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
docs
*.md
